      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:8:1:41:2",
      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " [إِنَّ] النَّاسَ طَبَقَاتٌ ثَلَاثٌ طَبَقَةٌ هُمْ مِنَّا وَ نَحْنُ مِنْهُمْ وَ طَبَقَةٌ يَتَزَيَّنُونَ بِنَا وَ طَبَقَةٌ يَأْكُلُ بَعْضُهُمْ بَعْضاً [بِنَا]."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "<a id=\"_Toc492473402\">H 14723</a> – Al-Husayn Bin Muhammad Al-Ashary, from Moalla Bin Muhammad, from Al-Hassan Bin Ali Al-Washaa, from Musanna, from Abu Baseer, who has narrated the following:",
          "<span class=\"first-chapter-phrase\"><span class=\"first-in-chapter character-a\">A</span>bu Abdullah</span><sup>asws</sup> has said that: ‘The people are of three levels – A level who are from us<sup>asws</sup> and we<sup>asws</sup> are from them; and a level who adorn themselves by us<sup>asws</sup> (our<sup>asws</sup> name); and a level who eat each other by us<sup>asws</sup> (our<sup>asws</sup> name)’. "
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "275. Al-Husayn Bin Muhammad Al-Ashary, from Mu‘alla Bin Muhammad, from Al-Hassan Bin Ali Al-Washaa, from Musanna, from Abu Baseer, who has narrated the following: Abu Abdullah (a.s.) has said that: ‘The people are of three levels – A level who are from us (a.s.) and we (a.s.) are from them; and a level who adorn themselves by us (a.s.) (our (a.s.) name); and a level who eat each other by us (a.s.) (our (a.s.) name)’."
        ]
      }
